  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to observe the effects of antihemostatic therapy including
      nonsteroidal antiinflammatory, anticoagulant and antiaggregant therapy and other patient and
      procedure related factors on the risk of endoscopic biliary sphincterotomy induced bleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
